WEBVTT

02:54:51.322 --> 02:54:54.492
But he's too clever a waterman.

02:54:55.326 --> 02:54:58.621
And if he alerts the enemy
to our whereabouts...

02:54:58.788 --> 02:55:01.081
...it will make the crossing
even more dangerous.

02:55:01.248 --> 02:55:03.292
SAM:
Have some food, Mr. Frodo.

02:55:03.459 --> 02:55:06.587
- No, Sam.
- You haven't eaten anything all day.

02:55:06.754 --> 02:55:09.840
You're not sleeping, neither.
Don't think I haven't noticed.
